{"tid":257203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國強：社會別以負面角度看高鐵","createTime":"2017-05-25T05:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T00:45:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3555be26bb4270b63d1976b0209f0529ea439711","tid":257203,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司司長袁國強指，希望公眾不要以負面角度看待高鐵一地兩檢安排。<br />\n<br />\n袁國強在英國會見傳媒時指中央官員和特區官員均有共識，高鐵往後的一地兩檢安排一定會符合基本法和一國兩制的原則。他認為，最重要是了解一地兩檢的本質和推行原因，而非以負面角度看待此事，又指最終安排會在適當時候公布。<br />\n<br />\n正身處倫敦的袁國強在「亞洲之家」發表演說，指基本法包含各項重要的憲法保障對維護司法獨立至為重要，亦是法治的基石之一，又指香港的法官不論在民事案件抑或具爭議性的公法案件，包括有關司法覆核申請的案件，都作出有理據的判決。"},{"pid":"7d5888ec0be943de7d97bffb8336f35bcf4b88a2","tid":257203,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=222434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D222434&d=3%2Fyb9fo0OzuLUwrjyftdmjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6d7707c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D222434&h=0d54aa6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=222434</a>"},{"pid":"938a236358a01a5bc437e556a69c1ba7ea5c0576","tid":257203,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"又賴公眾"},{"pid":"7283ba9828de1a5eefc42bfde8b9952c210b97ba","tid":257203,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:28:12.000Z","msg":"佢有邊方面係正架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6929446d89f0144bf1e6d32819ffa0b91a5ca18","tid":257203,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31571fc042f7cffb89bc97d4f1137e139524a7c8","tid":257203,"uid":84691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有邊方面係正架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚樣"},{"pid":"1a58e503a87fd697d2346efb812e6ca4edeb833d","tid":257203,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"高鐵：袁國強別以負面角度看社會"}]}